channel.title: Toms Cache Suit
channel.description:
Hello, I'm having some trouble with an error I'm receiving with Toms Cache Suit, I'm trying to edit my titelbox because it is black. That is not what I'm having trouble with though, I load my cache with the suit. Then I click View/Edit Image Archives, then Title and I get an error saying "An error has accord whilst loading archive: com.jagex.cache.util.exceptions.CacheException: File size too large. Could someone explain to me what is wrong? Or maybe point me into the direction of a new cache editor.
[IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/1620bns.jpg[/img]
On a side note, it doesn't edit anything else either.
